{"actor":"Joshua Oliphant","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-04-13T08:05:01Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":3,"issue_id":"link_content_scraper-c5q","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"link_content_scraper-c5q\",\"title\":\"Add tests for ProgressTracker, RateLimiter, and scraper module\",\"description\":\"Core async modules (progress.py, rate_limit.py, scraper.py) have zero direct test coverage. ProgressTracker has 10 methods (init, increment, cancel, generate_events, etc.) none tested directly. RateLimiter timing and concurrency behavior is untested. These are the most critical business logic modules.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"joshua.oliphant@hey.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-13T04:35:03Z\",\"created_by\":\"Joshua Oliphant\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-13T04:35:03Z\"}"}
